<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> وَأَلَّا يُفَرِّقَ بَيْنَهُمَا إِلَّا بِقَدْرِ إِقَامَةٍ، وَوُضُوءٍ خَفِيفٍ، فَيَبْطُلُ بِرَاتِبَةٍ بَيْنَهُمَا.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٣]</span> وَوُجُودُ العُذْرِ عِنْدَ افْتِتَاحِهِمَا، وَسَلَامِ الأُولَى.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٤]</span> وَاسْتِمْرَارُهُ -فِي غَيْرِ جَمْعِ مَطَرٍ وَنَحْوِهِ- إِلَى فَرَاغِ الثَّانِيَةِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- فَلَوْ أَحْرَمَ بِالأُولَى لِمَطَرٍ،<span style="color:#006d98"> ثُمَّ انْقَطَعَ وَلَمْ يَعُدْ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> فَإِنْ حَصَلَ وَحَلٌ:</span> لَمْ يَبْطُلْ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- وَإِلَّا بَطَلَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَإِنِ انْقَطَعَ سَفَرٌ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> بِأُولَى:</span> بَطَلَ الجَمْعُ وَالقَصْرُ، فَيُتِمُّهَا، وَتَصِحُّ فَرْضًا.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَبِثَانِيَةٍ:</span> بَطَلَا، وَيُتِمُّهَا نَفْلًا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَيُشْتَرَطُ لِجَمْعٍ بِوَقْتِ ثَانِيَةٍ:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> نِيَّتُهُ بِوَقْتِ أُولَى؛ مَا لَمْ يَضِقْ عَنْ فِعْلِهَا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> وَبَقَاءُ عُذْرٍ إِلَى دُخُولِ وَقْتِ الثَّانِيَةِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>لَا غَيْرُ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>- وَلَا يُشْتَرَطُ لِلصَّحَّةِ اتِّحَادُ إِمَامٍ وَمَأْمُومٍ،<span style="color:#006d98"> فَلَوْ صَلَّاهُمَا:</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>- خَلْفَ إِمَامَيْنِ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>